➜想体验幸福的滋味？炖一锅软嫩的蹄筋吧
http://www.sohu.com/a/431104719_354843	25401
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201111/8fac69a66b8241be82ad6ff7ce1199be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=223301089&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p>你知道什么是“120分的幸福感”吗？</p>
<p>小时候，放学饿着肚子回家，刚走到门口，闻到自家厨房窗口飘出浓郁的红烧牛肉香，脚下顿时蹦了起来，这是100分的幸福。</p>
<p>立刻冲进厨房一看，锅里奶奶炖的竟然是蹄筋！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201111/6abce917005a4caea86f6f00888bc637.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>那就是原地狂舞的120分幸福了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201111/23f0becee9f3482785b516058fb2c097.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
